{"type":"text","timestamp":1775839928488,"sessionID":"ses_287b2baffffecGB2s9iHjnUgJY","part":{"id":"prt_d784ecf93001KojS6RIGfbdQpn","messageID":"msg_d784ec4c1001LcPVf9y8msPzjh","sessionID":"ses_287b2baffffecGB2s9iHjnUgJY","type":"text","text":"已创建 AR-002 CodeInterpreter CRD 类型定义的 delta-spec.md 文件，包含以下 Requirements 和验收场景：\n\n1. **CodeInterpreter API type definition** - 类型定义和注册场景\n2. **CodeInterpreter status subresource** - 状态子资源和 phase 转换场景\n3. **CodeInterpreter phase and condition types** - 常量和条件类型场景\n4. **CodeInterpreter validation** - 验证逻辑场景（runtimeRef、code、language、resources）\n5. **CRD manifest generation** - CRD 清单生成场景\n6. **client-go typed client** -  typed client CRUD 操作场景\n7. **Informer factory** - Informer 工厂和事件处理场景\n8. **Lister** - Lister 查询场景\n9. **Fake clients** - 测试用 fake client 场景\n10. **Deepcopy generation** - DeepCopy 方法生成场景\n11. **Expansion interfaces** - 扩展接口场景\n12. **Scheme and codec registration** - Scheme 注册场景\n13. **Resource plural** - REST 资源复数命名场景","time":{"start":1775839928487,"end":1775839928487}}}
